  "detailed_description": "\"Hop Spring Girl\" is a 2D platform action game where you aim to reach the top by controlling hopping.<br>Determine the direction with the stick, adjust the jumping power at the timing of the jump, and overcome many difficulties.<br><br>The main character will jump up and down on her own, so be careful not to miss the timing of her jumps.<br>Once you jump, you can't control it until you land, so jump carefully and proceed.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897860/extras/1b3ffe689ece9031325ef4dc65faf573.poster.avif?t=1714552863\" width=702 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897860/extras/1b3ffe689ece9031325ef4dc65faf573.webm?t=1714552863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897860/extras/1b3ffe689ece9031325ef4dc65faf573.mp4?t=1714552863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Control direction with stick<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897860/extras/42bd8c421d363baa6b95c36c73fbb28a.poster.avif?t=1714552863\" width=614 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897860/extras/42bd8c421d363baa6b95c36c73fbb28a.webm?t=1714552863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897860/extras/42bd8c421d363baa6b95c36c73fbb28a.mp4?t=1714552863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Jumping power changes depending on timing",
